Reposted from @rbpf_pro PUBLIC BULLETIN: ASSITANCE WITH IDENTIFYING THIS INDIVIDUAL 

The Royal Barbados Police Force is seeking the assistance of the public in identifying the individual seen in this photograph. We are also seeking assistance in locating his next of kin. He was seen wandering around the Sir Winston Scott Polyclinic compound about 6:55 am on Wednesday 8th September 2021. He appears to be between the ages of 14-16 years and is non-verbal. He is about five (5) feet five (5) inches in height and dark complexion. He is wearing a green and white seamless jersey, a black three quarter pants and black slippers.

Anyone who can assists with identifying this individual is asked to contact the Hastings/Worthing Police Station at telephone number 430-7614.

Rodney Inniss Inspector (Ag.) 
Police Public Relations Officer 
Royal Barbados Police Force
